attributes.review: i cannot explain how terrible this app is. i went to the zoo to go pick up my pet alligator named home slice and he was so hungry so we went to costco to buy him some food but then i went to go ride home on the train to take home slice to go see his friend chocolate milk and the guy flying the train completely kicked us off and so i called this dude and he said that he had a flat tire so then we had to research the price of a tire to fit on a huge truck but the truck drivers didn’t know what that is so they called some of their buddies on the radio and then changed the station to 101.9kissFM and listened to some taylor swift but this app kept blowing up my phone with notifications and it was just so annoying i could not hear my taylor swift song and such spam that i had to delete it. i cannot tell you how much this ruined me and home slice’s day. extremely disappointed.
